    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence COU. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted because the ASTM F1717 standard specifies a single standardized test condition and the validation dataset (N=11, two labs) provides sufficient statistical confidence in the QoI comparisons. All three primary QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and < 10% difference acceptance criteria. Package integrity hash recorded; digital signature pending completion of organizational signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
